A script to help study CCI trade tactics.


Usage
=====

Just run `bin/cci` in your terminal.

Options, see 'bin/cci --help'


Examples
========

Minute resolution from begining of July with standard values for CCI

bin/cci -t -v --period 20 --factor 0.015 --resolution 60 --after 2015-07-01



Simulate CCI-trading for the last 4 hours (minute-wise), start with 0 shares, buy when crossing -150, sell when crossing 120

bin/cci -t -v --resolution 60 --only 240 --start_shares 0 --buy_cci -150 --sell_cci 120



BUGS
====

none :)
